                                        <div class="layer-content"><p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;"><b>Laax</b>&nbsp;(<span class="IPA-label IPA-label-small" style="font-size: 13.6px;">German:</span>&nbsp;<span class="IPA nowrap" lang="de-Latn-fonipa" style="text-wrap-mode: nowrap;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/Standard_German" title="Help:IPA/Standard German" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none !important;">[laːks]</a></span>;&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romansh_language" title="Romansh language" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Romansh</a>:&nbsp;<i lang="rm">Lags</i>,&nbsp;<span class="IPA-label IPA-label-small" style="font-size: 13.6px;">pronounced</span>&nbsp;<span class="IPA nowrap" lang="rm-Latn-fonipa" style="text-wrap-mode: nowrap;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/Romansh" title="Help:IPA/Romansh" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none !important;">[laks]</a></span>) is a&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Municipalities_of_Switzerland" title="Municipalities of Switzerland" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">municipality</a>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surselva_Region" title="Surselva Region" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Surselva Region</a>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Switzerland" title="Switzerland" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Swiss</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cantons_of_Switzerland" title="Cantons of Switzerland" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">canton</a>&nbsp;of&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graub%C3%BCnden" class="mw-redirect" title="Graubünden" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Graubünden</a>.</p><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2" style="color: rgb(16, 20, 24); margin-top: 0.25em; margin-bottom: 0.25em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; display: flow-root; word-break: break-word; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, &quot;Source Serif Pro&quot;, serif; line-height: 1.375;"><h2 id="History" style="color: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.25em; display: inline; word-break: break-word; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.375; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">History</h2><span class="mw-editsection" style="user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; margin-inline: 1em 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 0; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="color: rgb(84, 89, 93); margin-right: 0.25em; margin-inline: 0px 0.25em;">[</span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Laax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; overflow-wrap: break-word;">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket" style="color: rgb(84, 89, 93); margin-left: 0.25em; margin-inline: 0.25em 0px;">]</span></span></div><figure class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Thumb" style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-left: 1.4em; display: table; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 0; clear: right; float: right; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); color: rgb(32, 33, 34); min-width: 100px; font-family: sans-serif;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Siegel_Freie_von_Laax.JPG" class="mw-file-description" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; position: relative; border: 0px;"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Siegel_Freie_von_Laax.JPG/250px-Siegel_Freie_von_Laax.JPG" decoding="async" width="250" height="247" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Siegel_Freie_von_Laax.JPG/500px-Siegel_Freie_von_Laax.JPG 1.5x" data-file-width="1264" data-file-height="1250" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; margin: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(32, 33, 34); height: auto; max-width: calc(100% - 8px);"></a><figcaption style="display: table-caption; caption-side: bottom; background-color: inherit; line-height: 1.4em; word-break: break-word; text-align: start; padding-right: 6px; padding-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 6px; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; font-size: 14.144px;">Seal of the "Freie von Laax", 1727</figcaption></figure><table class="box-Expand_section plainlinks metadata ambox mbox-small-left ambox-content" role="presentation" style="font-size: 14.08px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 10px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(162, 169, 177) rgb(162, 169, 177) rgb(162, 169, 177) rgb(242, 133, 0); border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); margin-top: 4px; margin-right: 1em; margin-bottom: 4px; overflow: hidden; width: 238px; line-height: 1.25em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;"><tbody><tr><td class="mbox-image" style="border: none; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 0.5em; text-align: center;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Wiki_letter_w_cropped.svg" class="mw-file-description" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><img alt="[icon]" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/Wiki_letter_w_cropped.svg/20px-Wiki_letter_w_cropped.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="14" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/Wiki_letter_w_cropped.svg/40px-Wiki_letter_w_cropped.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="44" data-file-height="31" style="border: 0px;"></a></span></td><td class="mbox-text" style="border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.5em; width: 185.906px;"><div class="mbox-text-span">This section&nbsp;<b>needs expansion</b>. You can help by&nbsp;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Laax&amp;action=edit&amp;section=" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word; background: none !important;">adding to it</a>.&nbsp;<span class="date-container"><i>(<span class="date">March 2022</span>)</i></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;">Laax is first undoubtedly mentioned&nbsp;<abbr title="circa" style="border-bottom: 0px;">c.</abbr>&nbsp;1290–98 as&nbsp;<i>Lags</i>.<sup id="cite_ref-HDS_3-0" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap-mode: nowrap; font-size: 12.8px;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laax#cite_note-HDS-3" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span class="cite-bracket" style="pointer-events: none;">[</span>3<span class="cite-bracket" style="pointer-events: none;">]</span></a></sup></p><p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;">Laax is first mentioned indirectly in 765 AD when Bishop&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Tello_of_Chur&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Tello of Chur (page does not exist)" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(191, 60, 44); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Tello of Chur</a>&nbsp;granted his share of Flemme (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flims" title="Flims" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Flims</a>) to the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Disentis_Monastery&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Disentis Monastery (page does not exist)" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(191, 60, 44); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Disentis Monastery</a>, noting Laax in his will. The village appears in a 1290 register of the Cathedral of Chur and was officially independent by 1525 with its own parish church. In 1428, the&nbsp;<a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freie_von_Laax" class="extiw" title="de:Freie von Laax" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">de:Freie von Laax</a>&nbsp;bought their freedom from Count[&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Rudolf_VII_of_Werdenberg-Sargans&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Rudolf VII of Werdenberg-Sargans (page does not exist)" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(191, 60, 44); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Rudolf VII of Werdenberg-Sargans</a>, gaining unique autonomy, freedom, and privileges such as market rights and tolls. In 1677,&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Udalrich_de_Mont&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Udalrich de Mont (page does not exist)" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(191, 60, 44); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Udalrich de Mont</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bishop_of_Chur" title="Bishop of Chur" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Bishop of Chur</a>, consecrated the new church in Laax to the patrons&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint_Gallus" class="mw-redirect" title="Saint Gallus" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Saint Gallus</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint_Otmar" class="mw-redirect" title="Saint Otmar" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Saint Otmar</a>. Laax joined the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ilanz" title="Ilanz" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Ilanz</a>&nbsp;district in 1851 after the dissolution of the&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Laax-Seewis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Laax-Seewis (page does not exist)" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(191, 60, 44); background: none; border-radius: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word;">Laax-Seewis</a>&nbsp;court, and tourism began developing in 1962 with the opening of the Crap Sogn Gion.</p></div>
